column5: Anyone know where I can purchase a printed map of Lac Seul (or the sections of Lac Seul). I bought a nice one for Eagle Lake on Fishing Hot Spots, but I can't seem to find Lac Seul on there. Looking for recommendations. Thanks!

https://www.trakmaps.com/en/products...l-maps-charts/Look at the above link. You'll have to zoom in to see the available maps for any particular area.I have a printed Navionics map, but can't find it anymore. Most camps have some sort of map available.Pooch
Four Season's Sports in Ear Falls sells good printed maps of each section of Lac Seul Four Seasons Sport Shop 37 Mccallum St Ear Falls, ON P0V 1T0, Canada Phone: (807) 222-2200 RBF
Thanks much, looks like they have something. Just have to dig now and see if it's what I'm looking for. Very nice, thanks!
